## PART 9 — localStorage Keys (Browser)

```

KEY             VALUE                   SET BY          CLEARED BY

──────────────  ──────────────────────  ──────────────  ──────────────

we\_token        32-char session token   login()         logout() / clearAuth()

we\_userId       USR001 format           login()         logout() / clearAuth()

we\_playerName   player's display name   login()         logout() / clearAuth()

we\_role         "player" or "admin"     login()         logout() / clearAuth()



Pages that check these:

&nbsp; dashboard.html  → requireAuth() → redirects to login if no token

&nbsp; admin/panel.html → requireAdmin() → redirects if no token or role != admin

&nbsp; navbar (all pages) → shows Login/Register OR PlayerName/Dashboard based on token

